				<element type="warning_sequence">1</element>
                <text type="warning_situation">
				<p>MINOR FLOODING POSSIBLE AT OAKBANK FROM WEDNESDAY EVENING</p>

				<p/>
				<p>Moderate rainfall totals have been recorded over the Onkaparinga River catchment over the last few days, causing small river and creek rises.</p>
<p>Further rainfall is forecast for the remainder of Wednesday and into Thursday, which may cause the upper Onkaparinga River at Oakbank to exceed the minor flood level from Wednesday evening.</p>
<p>Note: The minor flood level at Oakbank was lowered from 2.10 m to 1.17 m in December 2025.</p>

				<p/>

                </text>
                <element type="severity">Minor</element>
